wterm - xterm for wayland
--------------------

wterm is an xterm replacement based on st, a simple terminal emulator for X
originally made by suckless.


Requirements
------------

    fontconfig
    wayland
    xkbcommon
    pixman
    libdrm

Install
--------

    make clean install

See the man page for additional details.

